      "raw_text": "What Would Jesus Do If the\nCity Council Should Forbid Him to\nSpeak On the Streets of SpOkane?\"\nThis has been chosen by Mrs. Flora\nM. Bilkiss, the jail missionary and\nSUM worker as the theme for an\nopen air sermon, which she an\nnounces she will preach on the va\ncant lot on Front avenue Just east\nOF Washington street, Sunday after\nnoon at 3 o'clock.\n\n\nMrs. Bilkiss was arrested the\nother day and arraigned in court\nTor attempting to speak at River\nside avenue and Howard street. She\nhad wrapped herself in the Ameri-\ncan flag and carried the bible. fig\nuring that in that armor she should\nbe immune from prosecution under\nthe anti-street speaking ordinance."
    }
